data.description: HUGE price reduction! Seller is also willing to contribute an additional $5,000 towards closing costs toward a rate buy-down, closing costs, or other expense of the buyer's choice. Open House Saturday and Sunday! This beautiful 5 bedroom, 3 bath home was built in 2021 and includes over $30,000 of improvements including enhanced lighting inside and out, USB-C plugs and upgraded fans throughout, gutters with leaf guards, epoxy finish in the garage, security system, and more. Why build new and have to spend money on sod, landscaping, window coverings, and so much more when this one is ready for you TODAY! Qualified buyers may be eligible for loan assumption with a LOW 3.875% interest rate (4.179% APR) and LOW MONTHLY PAYMENT - contact for details!
